data.description: This great home is back on the market! Hardwood flooring just refinished and looks GORGEOUS! Beautiful 3 bed, 2 bath home on over TWO acres and a pond! Come tour this beautiful West Columbia home only ten minutes to downtown Columbia! Walk inside to find a formal dining room with built in cabinetry to your left and huge formal living to your right with a brick surround fireplace. Hardwood floors flow throughout the common areas, with carpet only in the bedrooms. Head into your kitchen that hosts white cabinetry and plenty of cabinet space and a pantry for storage. The master bedroom has plenty of closet space and a private bathroom. The secondary bedrooms share a bath. Towards the back of the house is a large living area overlooking the pond. Walk through your large mudroom with plenty of windows for sunlight onto a deck overlooking the pond. This home has a double depth garage accessible from the back of the house and a detached one car garage. Come see this beautiful home today!
